title: Bump Svg.Skia from 1.0.0 to 1.0.0.1
body:
Bumps [Svg.Skia](https://github.com/wieslawsoltes/Svg.Skia) from 1.0.0 to 1.0.0.1.
Commits
  • d493643 Fix version
  • 9ed0377 Handle double close commands
  • 5352235 Update Base.props
  • 79b3d4c Handle close after move command
  • d76590e Handle consequent move commands
  • 2b36da2 Format code
  • 1f10870 Add try/catch block
  • 41a5e6a Merge pull request #129 from atjn/patch-1
